pg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Killers-Of-The-Flower-Moon-Press-shot@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Killers-Of-The-Flower-Moon-Press-shot@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Killers-Of-The-Flower-Moon-Press-shot@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Killers-Of-The-Flower-Moon-Press-shot@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/leonardo-dicaprio">，莱昂纳多·迪卡普里奥</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/killers-of-the-flower-moon-review-martin-scorsese-3448518#:~:text=The%20film%20focuses%20on%20two,Osage%20people%20about%20the%20place."><em>《花月杀手》</em></a>中的片酬已经曝光。</p><p>据<a href="https://puck.news/newsletter_content/what-im-hearing-the-next-strike-elon-the-movie-disneys-slasher-strategy-2/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《Puck News》报道</em></a>，这位演员凭借饰演主角欧内斯特·伯克哈特 (Ernest Burkheart) 的表演获得了 4000 万美元（3250 万英镑）的收入。就背景而言，该电影的总制作预算估计约为 2 亿美元（1.629 亿英镑）。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-interviews/martin-scorsese-killers-of-the-flower-moon-3516541">马丁·斯科塞斯的智慧：“我必须经历一切才能学习”</a></strong></li></ul><p>目前尚不清楚当<em>《花月杀手》</em>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/apple-tv">Apple TV+</a>上上映时，迪卡普里奥是否会根据电影的票房表现或残差获得奖金。该公司尚未宣布这部电影在流媒体平台上的上映日期。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/general-news/leonardo-dicaprio-makes-how-movie-783859/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《好莱坞报道》报道</em></a>，迪卡普里奥因在 2014 年与<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/martin-scorsese">马丁·斯科塞斯</a>合作的<em>《华尔街之狼》</em>中扮演角色而获得了 2500 万美元（2030 万英镑）的预付片酬。然而，这也包括他的制作费，而预算超支意味着他不得不推迟部分工资。 </p><figure id="attachment_3425227" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3425227" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3425227" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/u